                  <p className="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">직원, 거래처, 고정 지출 항목을 관리하여 더 정교한 AI 분석 리포트를 받아보세요.</p>
                </div>
                <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                  <button onClick={() => setIsStaffModalOpen(true)} className="p-6 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all text-left">
                    <div className="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 mb-4">
                      <svg className="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <span className="font-black text-sm block">직원 관리</span>
                    <span className="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-bold">인건비 자동 안분</span>
